public/
# Zola 0.22's Giallo highlighter writes its generated theme stylesheet
# into static/ (not just public/) as a `zola build` side effect when
# [markdown.highlighting] style = "class" — verified against the
# installed zola 0.22.1 binary. Unused here: static/css/syntax.css
# supplies this site's own three-ink pass over the emitted classes
# instead of this stock theme's colors (config.toml's own comment has
# the full note). Regenerates deterministically on every build; never
# hand-edit it.
